description: Swimmers can return to the water for the first time since the island's pools were closed in March.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man swimming pools reopen
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man swimming pools reopen - BBC News
maintext: Mr Holland said younger swimmers had been learning how to "converse with one another" again after months of lockdown measures and he was "glad to see them taking time to spend with their team".
